Document: TextParagraph
Path: godot/classes/class_textparagraph.rst
Summary: This section lists the properties available for configuring a TextParagraph object.

* alignment (HorizontalAlignment). Default: 0.
* break_flags (bitfield[LineBreakFlag]). Default: 3.
* custom_punctuation (String). Default: "".
* direction (Direction). Default: 0.
* ellipsis_char (String). Default: "…".
* justification_flags (bitfield[JustificationFlag]). Default: 163.
* line_spacing (float). Default: 0.0.
* max_lines_visible (int). Default: -1.
* orientation (Orientation). Default: 0.
* preserve_control (bool). Default: false.
* preserve_invalid (bool). Default: true.
* text_overrun_behavior (OverrunBehavior). Default: 0.
* width (float). Default: -1.0.
